{"type": "article", "id": 10107, "title": "“必胜客劲片盒” 披萨包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-28T07:24:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235533owRxJ5rBen48cNOd.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t奥美集团和必胜客联合推出了一款“必胜客劲片盒”的披萨包装，他们在普通的必胜客盒子的基础上，打开了一个圆形小孔，以及一个装嵌在底座上的塑料镜片，用户取下孔盖，把镜片安装进去，扫描盒子上的二维码，就可以在“必胜客劲片精选”中挑选自己喜欢的影片播放。这是两方合作在香港推行的一次创新产品活动，上个月在测试中市场反应极好，目前已经决定在香港其他地区广泛推广。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235529rQhjo5VkUi3MFem7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7396088\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235530EAP9UqoHRVgkNsIF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235530DOsxkV7juHWa259R.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235531m0JacGoeUVAYf18k.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235531IpzgtQlaRjYJW9sw.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235532tTKBYqmxR09k83WM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235532ydgTN8J70Zwi4Qjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}